ng 384w,\n/static/f1fe4df4460b65951a8551bf9b23bc34/a1448/campus2.png 485w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/f1fe4df4460b65951a8551bf9b23bc34/a1448/campus2.png\" alt=\"campus2.png\" title=\"campus2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n</div>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>프로젝트 1. 페어플레이</strong></p>\n<figure>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 576px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 139.58333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/a59e9/pairplay1.webp 192w,\n/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/0ca9f/pairplay1.webp 384w,\n/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/f1c97/pairplay1.webp 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/3b721/pairplay1.png 192w,\n/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/66595/pairplay1.png 384w,\n/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/694da/pairplay1.png 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/0d8e473073a305db74d59b7620d110a0/694da/pairplay1.png\" alt=\"pairplay1\" title=\"pairplay1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>가장 최근에 진행했던 Pairplay</strong>에서는 기능 폴더 > 각 페이지 폴더 > 해당 컴포넌트 순으로 정리하였다.</p>\n<p>또한 자주 사용되는 푸터나 헤더와 같은 공통 요소들은 common 폴더에 정리하여 다른 팀원들과 함께 사용할 수 있었다.</p>\n<h1>Source</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://shop.bradfrost.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://shop.bradfrost.com/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://kciter.so/posts/effective-atomic-design\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://kciter.so/posts/effective-atomic-design</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fe-developers.kakaoent.com/2022/220505-how-page-part-use-atomic-design-system/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://fe-developers.kakaoent.com/2022/220505-how-page-part-use-atomic-design-system/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2C1tXVHu9XQ&#x26;t=244s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2C1tXVHu9XQ&#x26;t=244s</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"프론트엔드에서 컴포넌트 구성은?(작성중)","summary":"프론트엔드 컴포넌트 설계 패턴 중 아토믹 디자인은...","date":"2022.06.28.","categories":["Web Frontend","TIL","Design"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8d8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/8a036/atomic-design.png","srcSet":"/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/2a9e9/atomic-design.png 256w,\n/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/c7bd0/atomic-design.png 512w,\n/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/8a036/atomic-design.png 1024w","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/36766/atomic-design.webp 256w,\n/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/a79fe/atomic-design.webp 512w,\n/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/2d898/atomic-design.webp 1024w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw"}]},"width":1024,"height":768}},"publicURL":"/static/9b67dbfd80a963759427128d5232cf74/atomic-design.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Atomic Design/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}